{"tid":473192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好想離開香港呢個光怪陸離既地方","createTime":"2017-11-19T04:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T09:14:06.000Z","uid":78349,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d1430edcb21633c0bcf7d110e18b799319870a57","tid":473192,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出呢個post 我可能比人放入五毛名單<br />\n<br />\n但係我想問下 <br />\n樓又買唔起 無辦法組織家庭<br />\n空氣差 日日索支那工業廢氣<br />\n國歌法 廿三條 人大䆁法 <br />\n所有公共部門做野求其<br />\n人口越來越多 冇相關措施配合下<br />\n食水有鉛 最近仲有瀝青 都話可以安全飲用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打壓啲小市民就不遺餘力 地產權貴就拎哂著數<br />\n醫療 新症公立可以等幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所有公共政策都只係幫緊最撚窮個班<br />\n中間個堆就乜都無 其實本身都冇乜錢淨<br />\n<br />\n而政府係唔會理蟻民既死活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日有學生跳樓wfc?<br />\n<br />\n利申：希望考到專業資格後移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202eee6cd1937f4d35290213693948d14fddf5d6","tid":473192,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fdea46aa7eadf23b7df48b73fcebe1a20306c5","tid":473192,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:30:41.000Z","msg":"想移民去邊?"},{"pid":"81d323ae781b13de4b5225ca076e0b7d08b12be5","tid":473192,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:32:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想移民去邊?</blockquote><br />\n考慮緊澳洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為有分加 入藉應該無問題<br />\n但係自己未去過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16121316aeabd6d22463944c73a84e0b88bed559","tid":473192,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:35:13.000Z","msg":"澳洲排華都嚴重㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c407d97bc8b949303e964e1d998578948d89aa","tid":473192,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳洲排華都嚴重㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個都係考慮因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉"},{"pid":"fb3352cf979ddd5f470a353e2e7c8b879ddc9532","tid":473192,"uid":155725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:51:37.000Z","msg":"其實只要有錢，住香港會好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無考慮喺香港努力搵一大筆之後去低生活指數既地方生活？"},{"pid":"da8ff76d5cb09713d4917846fe80102ced8d9923","tid":473192,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實只要有錢，住香港會好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無考慮喺香港努力搵一大筆之後去低生活指數既地方生活？</blockquote><br />\n首先你要發到達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有樓有車生活緊係唔洗煩架"},{"pid":"2e86aa85277ee8f60ab0a1adfa71609f5e6b49c4","tid":473192,"uid":27617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:56:22.000Z","msg":"正皮俾光怪陸離"},{"pid":"5e0ad40745b0b92475152787594275fa6f7a634c","tid":473192,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>澳洲排華都嚴重㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個都係考慮因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉</blockquote><br />\n不如試下適應香港社會算啦！我咁講實有好多人話我港豬，但話人港豬嗰班又咪每日硬着頭皮適應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慢慢就慣"},{"pid":"effbdd7ea4980a1bdf853f95693d71d7a284a623","tid":473192,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>澳洲排華都嚴重㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個都係考慮因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉</blockquote><br />\n不如試下適應香港社會算啦！我咁講實有好多人話我港豬，但話人港豬嗰班又咪每日硬着頭皮適應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慢慢就慣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e7a087e0894d89fb94cc97509411dd3215f8de","tid":473192,"uid":14642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:13:02.000Z","msg":"已絕望"},{"pid":"11101bfa042889843b64210a072cc9c72a76063b","tid":473192,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:13:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實只要有錢，住香港會好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無考慮喺香港努力搵一大筆之後去低生活指數既地方生活？</blockquote><br />\n諗起前排有單新聞講有個家庭去咗泰國住，獨立屋揸靚車，日日炒股維生"},{"pid":"40dcd2ac456dca0d07f1466a20b6f1ffacc60c8f","tid":473192,"uid":28054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實只要有錢，住香港會好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無考慮喺香港努力搵一大筆之後去低生活指數既地方生活？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有錢住邊到都舒服架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f96179c39d00498fca5f508cf652a993d90dbfd","tid":473192,"uid":115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實只要有錢，住香港會好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無考慮喺香港努力搵一大筆之後去低生活指數既地方生活？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有錢住邊到都舒服架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係香港要好撚好撚好撚有錢先舒服<br />\n其他地區只需要好撚有錢<br />\n明唔撚明呀？<br />\n<br />\n簡單d講，假設你有1000萬<br />\n係香港買2層普通既樓已經完左<br />\n係外國係可以退休唔撚洗做了"}]}